Fans worldwide welcome Ronald Koeman back to Barcelona, as the head coach of the team. “Barca fans and this community would like to congratulate you and thank you for your willingness to take over this mess” “You played for us and now you’re going to coach the first team. We are here to support you in every way possible.” “Welcome to the Barca coaching family. Your experience promises to be enriching, challenging and rewarding.” “Success all the way man! A new dawn is here pls all he need is our love and support..Forca Barcelona” Welcome to Barca! Let’s see what you’ve got, Koeman! Good luck!